1 ]drug testing product or equipment used in accordance with paragraph (c)1. of
2 this subsection that contains residual or trace amounts of a synthetic opioid or
3 an analogue thereof shall not be prosecuted as possession of a controlled
4 substance under [any provision of ]this chapter.
5 (8) Any person who violates [any provision of ]this section shall be guilty of a Class A
6 misdemeanor.
